Text: The registration key won't work for me. Has anyone gotten it to work?
You must uninstall game and install again and then enter code it will work. It works for me on WIN7 64bit.

The registration key will work if you delete a file first.

-> You need to go to c:\users\"your username"\documents\deluxe ski jump 3\registration
--> Delete the file called registration.CFG
---> Now try to use the serial one more time
